  "body": "> [!NOTE]\r\n> This release contains the same changes as in release `1.63.1`. Release `1.63.1` is not flawed in any way.\r\n\r\n# Components\r\n\r\n## Application Security Management (IAST)\r\n\r\n* :sparkles::zap: Improve performance of regexps in IAST and query obfuscator (#11710 - @manuel-alvarez-alvarez)\r\n\r\n## Continuous Integration Visibility\r\n\r\n* :sparkles: Support Maven generateTestClasspath lookup on 3.6.0+ (#11634 - @daniel-mohedano)\r\n\r\n## Dynamic Instrumentation\r\n\r\n* :bug: Fix sampling log probe with capture expressions (#11628 - @jpbempel)\r\n\r\n## OpenFeature\r\n\r\n* :bug: Skip malformed FFE flags during config parsing (#11648 - @PerfectSlayer)\r\n",
